data.title: Jill Hennessy Movies and Shows
data.meta_description: Learn about Jill Hennessy on Apple TV. Browse shows and movies that feature Jill Hennessy including Wild Hogs, Madame Web, and more.
data.text:
Moriah

A father confronts the limits of unconditional love when he discovers his own teenage son may be planning an unimaginable crime.

Two of a Kind

Ed, Danny, and Mike combine forces with the team of Dr. Jordan Cavanaugh and Det. Woody Hoyt (from "Crossing Jordan") to solve a murder. Meanwhile, Snoop Dogg is trying to convince Delinda to allow his music video to film at the Montecito.

Double Down, Triple Threat

When a card counter's daughter is abducted, Danny, Mike, and Ed are reunited with Dr. Jordan Cavanaugh to solve a high-stakes kidnapping scheme. Meanwhile, Sam and Det. Woody Hoyt retrace their steps as to how they wound up in bed together.

The One Percent

Alicia manages the fallout when her client's insensitive statements to the press threaten the fate of a multi-billion dollar merger. Meanwhile, Diane faces a potential conflict of interest when she and Louis Canning are on opposite sides of a class action suit involving a pharmaceutical company. Also, Eli learns the truth about Alicia and Peter's relationship. Michael J. Fox returns as Louis Canning. Tom Skerritt reprises his role as Fortune 500 CEO James Paisley. Jill Hennessy returns as Rayna Hecht.
